Package parameter_estimation

Class Summary
CKEmulation CKEmulation is designed as a Thread type, implying that multiple CKEmulations can be initiated, allowing multithreading and possible speed-up
CKEmulation can call several Chemkin routines: Chem, CKReactorPlugFlow, GetSolution, GetSolnTranspose depending on the task to be executed
In order to cope with a limited number of Chemkin licenses, a counting Semaphore type is used to keep track of the number of licenses in use

Paths Paths contains paths to directories, files that are important in the Parameter Estimation program
Paths serves as a supertype to Param_Est, CKPackager, Rosenbrock types
